# Persona‑Aware AI Agent Suite (Demo)

> Thin‑slice proof‑of‑concept for a trio of gRPC/HTTP agents that personalize an e‑commerce design experience in real time.

## Components
| Service | Tech | Purpose |
|---------|------|---------|
| PersonaClassifier | FastAPI + torchserve (stub) | Classifies visitor persona in <150 ms |
| ProductAdvisor | Coming soon | Recommends plan / tutorial |
| ExperimentationBandit | Thompson Sampling notebook | Allocates traffic to best‑performing variant |
| Creative Concierge | Streamlit | Embeds in client site, swaps hero + CTA |

Run the stack:

```bash
docker compose up --build
